There were still voices similar to those in the UK before entry into the market of companies such as Tesco Mobile or Virgin Mobile.
However, it has proven that there is room for such providers and that they can really be successful.
By the way, you don't have to look for examples for a long time.
In February this we reported about the start of the virtual provider Mobilking in Poland.
